{"id":365775,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/10/机智的当当网：那些即将买不到的书/","date":"2014-10-12T09:03:51Z","modified":"2016-12-15T01:23:15Z","title":"机智的当当网：那些即将买不到的书","content":"<p>背景新闻：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2014/10/bbc%EF%BD%9C%E7%BD%91%E4%BC%A0%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%81%E6%9D%80%E4%BD%99%E8%8B%B1%E6%97%B6%E3%80%81%E4%B9%9D%E6%8A%8A%E5%88%80%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6-2/\">BBC｜网传中国封杀余英时、九把刀多名作家</a></p>\n<blockquote><p>中国有微博爆料说，广电总局向出版社下达通知，余英时、九把刀等作家的书全面下架，野夫、茅于轼、张千帆、梁文道、许知远等的书不予出版。</p>\n<p>中国新浪、腾讯等网站报道，有认证为出版人的微博称，通过相关会议材料获知了上述消息。</p>\n<p>消息说，封杀原因未知，但被怀疑可能和他们的政治立场有关。</p>\n<p>新浪娱乐报道说，已经联系到了多家出版社均表示已收到通知，消息属实。</p></blockquote>\n<p>以销售图书起家的当当网迅速并机智地为上述作家的作品制作了<a href=\"http://book.dangdang.com/20141011_mfyx\">这样一个专题页面</a>：</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang-1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-365778\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang-1.png\" alt=\"dangdang 1\" width=\"550\" height=\"1017\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang-1.png 803w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang-1-162x300.png 162w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang-1-553x1024.png 553w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang2.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-365779\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang2.png\" alt=\"dangdang2\" width=\"550\" height=\"858\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang2.png 803w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang2-192x300.png 192w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang2-656x1024.png 656w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang3.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-365780\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang3.png\" alt=\"dangdang3\" width=\"550\" height=\"670\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang3.png 798w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang3-246x300.png 246w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang4-copy.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-365781\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang4-copy.png\" alt=\"dangdang4 copy\" width=\"550\" height=\"521\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang4-copy.png 794w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2014/10/dangdang4-copy-300x284.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[13091,22737,10865,16666,9925,11848]}